item.dc:creator: @bhpkyeah satesql
item.description:
@bhpkyeah wrote:

[quote=“m.dog311, post:10, topic:264445”][quote author=Gamerstips link=topic=349194.msg2684788#msg2684788 date=1235601432]

This thread is full of fail.

fixt.

You dont like it?
[/quote]
Not at all. Not only is it a massively hardcoded mess, but it’s also wL based. You have more than likely added everything the easy way instead of the efficient way (based on the fact that you have used a wL source), and it also looks like you have continued to support the overused “Edgeville is the best home choice” statement. The things you have classified as “funny” are not funny at all. You’re “Santa Outfit” just proves that you know how to change a player into an npc (which is very easy considering most servers come with a method to do so). Your Member’s shop looks absolutely disgusting, just another downfall to hardcoding. Overall, your server is just like every other one.[/quote]

What is it about you that hates WL servers? You know its not hard to program WL to run efficient, send data to mysql, create program manager to manage, data. rewrite a lot of terrible written scripts , fix all the bugs, that made the server crash… Any p server, is gonna be buggy. And there’s not p server I haven’t been on that didn’t have some kind of bug… Now what I do wish is kids would stop using delta, and move onto something else…
